title: Thanksgiving Decorative Harvest Fall Mesh Wrap Rolls of Ribbon 5 Yards Each for Floral Arrangements Wreaths and Craft Party Supplies Decorations in Orange Green Brown & Yellow Colors by Gift Boutique
features: Includes 4 assorted Thanksgiving themed colors 1 of each Orange, Green, Brown & Yellow shot through with threads of Metallic tinsel Strands.
Add your creative touch to décor items, gift wrap, gift baskets, floral designs, party decorating and your Harvest Party will shimmer and sparkle with these Mesh rolls!

These rolls of glamorous mesh fabric is a stunning way to create gorgeous table runners for your DIY Fall Dinner. Your guest tables will pop and your centerpieces will look even more elegant. Cut it to size and create your own place mats, or use it as a draping for your arch. Create gorgeous floral arrangements, Wreaths and Bows for your Autumn home décor. It's a must-have crafting supply with so many uses.
Easy to bend and fold and keeps its shape. Use floral pins or metal Craft wire to pin mesh to foam or to attach to a round wire wreath frame!
Each roll measures 6" wide by 5 yards in length. Total of 60 feet.
